menu "SD / SPIFFS WAV"
    config USE_SPIFFS_WAV
        bool "Phat WAV tu SPIFFS (khong can the SD)"
        default y
        help
            Bat: mount SPIFFS, phat /spiffs/music.wav (file duoc dong goi khi flash).
            Tat: dung the SD nhu cu (SPI + FAT).

    config SD_FORMAT_IF_MOUNT_FAILED
        bool "Tu dong format the SD neu mount FAT that (XOA HET DU LIEU TREN THE)"
        default n
        help
            Chi dung khi tat SPIFFS WAV. Nguy hiem: se format lai the neu FAT loi.
endmenu
